{"tid":323684,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[年經][HKU] HKU HALL CULTURE 綜合討論區","createTime":"2017-07-15T19:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T03:34:53.000Z","uid":19724,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"981d3112c3498995d1d28800779af140fb101b06","tid":323684,"uid":19724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T19:06:01.000Z","msg":"年年依個時候都實有POST講HKU既HALL CULTURE, 今年終於有得SHARE<br />\n <br />\n 首先HKU既HALL可以分為3類: 最傳統, 傳統, HEA <br />\n最傳統: st john&rsquo;s, ricci, 何東, u hall <br />\n傳統: swire, sky lee, starr, wei lun, hysan, r c lee <br />\nHEA: suen chi sun, Morrison, lee shau kee <br />\n<br />\n而入到HALL之後都一定要玩唔同類型既活動<br />\n , 可分為sports/cultural <br />\nsports方面: 除左足球籃球嗰D, HKU有3種NEW BALL: softball, hockey, lacrosse <br />\n大部分HALL都較focus on new ball, 因為大部分人都未玩過, 唔會俾人屈<br />\n<br />\n點玩就自己睇wiki啦 <br />\nCultural就得4種: bridge, choir, debate, drama <br />\n間間HALL都focus on唔同方面, 所以要做足功課先好入<br />\n<br />\n分別簡單講吓D HALL既特色先: <br />\nSt john&rsquo;s <br />\n歷史最耐既HALL, 全部單人房 <br />\n專收靚仔靚女, 有錢人, 名校仔, 簡單D黎講就係精英<br />\n <br />\n你唔係有錢的話, 俾你符碌入到去都會好痛苦 <br />\nSt john&rsquo;s 係無focus, 因為佢sports同cultural都可以話係最勁 <br />\n如果你sports勁就全力玩sports, vice versa 大約要玩2-3隊 <br />\n<br />\nRicci <br />\n歷史最耐既男HALL, 全部單人房 <br />\n好多sports既勁人, 肯報就入到, 因為太chur <br />\nRicci focus on sports, 入去要玩2-3隊sports, 其中一樣要係new ball <br />\nCultural 喺ricci係毫無地位可言<br />\n<br />\n何東 <br />\n唯一一間女HALL <br />\n較多sports既勁人, 肯報就入到, 因為太chur <br />\n何東focus on sports, 入去要玩2-3隊sports, 其中一樣要係new ball <br />\n<br />\nU hall <br />\n男HALL <br />\n咩人都有, 肯報就入到, 因為太chur <br />\nU hall focus on new ball 同cultural, 入去要玩1隊new ball, 1-2隊cultural <br />\n另外值得一題既係時事<br />\n<br />\n佢地會有定期既forum俾hall mate互相share對各時事議題既睇法"},{"pid":"2810978b9fe790cb9e0a1f2c15bd6f861aa65a06","tid":323684,"uid":19724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T19:08:09.000Z","msg":"SWIRE <br />\nOk多人報, 因為喺campus入面好拎方便, hall community中存在感較低<br />\n較focus on cultural, esp choir <br />\n入去大約要玩1隊sport, 1隊cultural <br />\n<br />\nSky lee <br />\n好拎多人報, 因為喺campus入面, 仲要喺正中間, 好拎方便<br />\n無咩focus, 但new ball愈來愈勁 <br />\n入去大約要玩1隊sport, 1隊cultural <br />\nPs 唔知點解坊間對sky lee既評價都較差, 包括CHUR同不近人情 <br />\n<br />\nStarr <br />\n好拎多人報, 因為近campus, 同埋有平民版st john&rsquo;s之稱, 好多地區名校仔<br />\n <br />\n無咩focus, 但new ball愈來愈勁 <br />\n入去大約要玩1隊sport, 1隊cultural, 可HEA可唔HEA <br />\n<br />\nWei lun <br />\n唔算多人報, 近medic campus, 正正常常肯報就入到, 因為chur <br />\nFocus on sports, 包括new ball <br />\n入去大約要玩1-2隊sports, 多數包括1隊new ball <br />\nCultural 無咩地位 <br />\nPs 唔知點解坊間對wei lun既評價都較差, 包括CHUR同淫亂(但我唔覺淫亂) <br />\n<br />\nHysan <br />\nOk多人報, 近medic campus, 有部分人幾champ <br />\n較focus on sports, 包括new ball <br />\n入去大約要玩1-2隊sports, 1隊cultural <br />\n<br />\nR c lee <br />\n唔算多人報, 近medic campus, 正正常常肯報就入到, 因為存在感較低<br />\n無咩focus, sport同cultural都無咩特別<br />\n入去玩1隊sport/cultural就得<br />\n如果唔係成立歷史/地理位置問題, 應該歸類為HEA先岩"},{"pid":"4587968ee1adc9db634a4cd25f9d0df7fbf61622","tid":323684,"uid":19724,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T19:14:55.000Z","msg":"補充返<br />\n<br />\nSt john&rsquo;s <br />\n有一種好得意既氣場 <br />\n單獨一個唔會有好大既感覺,但當一班JOHN民出現既時候 <br />\nO個種自以為高人一等既氣場就會出現 <br />\n院訓一條&quot;Legend&quot; <br />\n入得去一定要係對ST JOHN有貢獻,幫HALL丁成為LEGEND先得 <br />\n所以有錢,SPORT勁,名校生差唔多係基本 <br />\n而ST John據我所知係SA最大,tutor O個D真係WFC <br />\nST JOHN同RICCI就最敵對,因為SPORT FIGHT得好勁 <br />\nBTW ST JOHN見sports scholar係即有offer <br />\n<br />\nRicci <br />\n一班男人,最中意打波,咩波都要威 <br />\n係CHUR,因為要贏,你明啦 <br />\n<br />\n何東 <br />\n女HALL,一係正女一係B <br />\n正女多過佢鄰居 <br />\n好focus係sports,好chur <br />\n何東妹比人既感覺係好獨立既女仔 <br />\nO既時候會有一日同ricci仔玩水戰 <br />\n<br />\nU hall <br />\n有HKU最好既HALL BUILDING同最多人一齊訓既房 <br />\n都重SPORT <br />\n而且都因為長歷史,成日都有名人番去sharing <br />\n<br />\nSWIRE真係係HALL界較靜 <br />\n不過知道佢地HALL係好多野玩 <br />\n都有出黎報HALL既比賽 <br />\n算係幾自成一角 <br />\n<br />\nSKY <br />\nSELL 家的感覺 <br />\nD人好CLOSE <br />\n主要因為個building design得好 <br />\npantry係正中間 <br />\n唔似新D既HALL咁ISOLATE <br />\nSKYERS 既人多數都好nice <br />\n係HALL到大家會好比心機為HALL,因為SELL家 <br />\n所以大家都會為家做好 <br />\n<br />\nSTARR <br />\n曾經好正,因為好似又有野玩又唔逼你玩,仲玩得幾好 <br />\nHALL界見到女仔TEAM就上緊,好似想傳型係HALL界做好D <br />\n<br />\n沙宣道HYSAN同WL其實好似 <br />\n傳統HALL多數好重NEW BALL,而且CHUR <br />\n所以有好多本身OLD BALL勁既人會去HYSAN WL <br />\n所以佢地兩間HALL OLD BALL都好好 <br />\n而NEW BALL因為肯比資源同有人LEAD,所以都唔差 <br />\n而其中一間仲係男女同層,同其他HALL既生活又唔同D <br />\n<br />\nRC係鐘庭耀攸WARDEN <br />\n所以HALL SA好自由,好多野都會搞 <br />\n但係就點都比唔上汁邊2間咁 <br />\n但係比上不足比下有突 <br />\n<br />\n二村男HALL <br />\n呢間真係無咩好講 <br />\n佢地唔多PARTI HALL界,雖然就黎100年 <br />\n但都無咩聲 <br />\n但佢地都係自己玩得開心 <br />\n另外有件事好就係同SCS好近 <br />\n而SCS又多女女,所以.... <br />\nANYWAY,其實好啱高登仔 <br />\n<br />\nSCS <br />\n一間係CULT上緊既HALL <br />\n可能新,TEAM既野未發展得好 <br />\n但野就好新,住係一流 <br />\n而且D人都肯CHUR(同比SA CHUR唔同) <br />\n所以應該就可能就快係HALL成績上追到一村既新HALL <br />\n<br />\nLSK <br />\n好自己既選擇自己既興趣 <br />\n唔強逼,輕鬆無壓力 <br />\n其實呢D都係我一個人既感覺,未必準 <br />\n住HALL一定好多野玩,都係睇係你想玩咩定係有一CHUR係玩"},{"pid":"8b7304296b88edbf426d50ba68baaabb9122f7e3","tid":323684,"uid":19724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T19:16:50.000Z","msg":"morrison <br />\n男HALL <br />\n出名毒, 十分適合高登仔<br />\n唔算多人報, 因為出名GAY同毒<br />\n , 但勝在夠HEA <br />\n入到去玩1-2隊team就ok<br />\n<br />\nsuen chi sun <br />\ncultural, esp drama幾出名 <br />\n好拎多人報, 因為HEA得黎又好似幾好玩 <br />\n入到去玩1-2隊team就ok<br />\n<br />\nlee shau kee <br />\n無住HALL既人都一定聽過, 因為出名最HEA, 所以都好拎多人報<br />\n有部分人更加因為HEA得滯走左<br />\n入到去玩1-2隊team就ok<br />\n單求宿位的話以上幾間真係唔錯<br />\n 但唔好唸住學到野"},{"pid":"50c124b6351d777918c5b7cb66e9b472726970eb","tid":323684,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T20:13:13.000Z","msg":"M hall睇唔睇gdp入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9a14f2fc44494b3561ecbb7252e4daa5790386","tid":323684,"uid":19724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:45:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>M hall睇唔睇gdp入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔睇，夠毒就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0fb629e7ec1b31ae7d798975038880251a3495","tid":323684,"uid":118915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:59:08.000Z","msg":"有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66a758dcbf791c2c14d549670cd47ffeb1a56ec","tid":323684,"uid":19724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:02:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ef958a4b29bc90724eaa6ed7e7dbd6e1427afd","tid":323684,"uid":118915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:04:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講哂啦嘛 new comer入黎睇左就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc94307db85cb4917ad2ad22aaa875abe72b29c2","tid":323684,"uid":33422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:04:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n垃圾hall<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打埋近年醜聞先有嘢討論"},{"pid":"2ce774e5602f8d86435e6a33dd5ed9e44e0ff4b5","tid":323684,"uid":19724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n垃圾hall<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打埋近年醜聞先有嘢討論</blockquote><br />\nSky Lee: JJ打面<br />\nSJC: 滴臘<br />\nS